text.value: Je una QR code yenye namba yako ya utambulisho?
Andika namba yako ya utambulisho yenye herufi tatu hapa
Scan QR code yako yenye namba ya utambulisho
### Taarifa za Utambulisho na idadi ya watu za Kaya na Mkuu wa kaya
Unaonekana kuwa kwenye kijiji ambacho hakipo kwenye taarifa za awali.
Inaonekana upo kwenye kitongoji ambacho hakipo kwenye database.
Hakiki herufi hizi za utambulisho za kitongoji ambacho upo
Hakiki herufi hizi za utambulisho za kitongoji ambacho upo
Kwasababu Kitongoji ulichopo hakipo kwenye Taarifa za awali, Msimbo wake utakuwa ni "XXX". Tafadhali wasiliana na Makao makuu kabla ya kuendelea.
Andika tarakimu 6 za nambari ya utambulisho wa kaya hapa.
Jumuisha alama ya dash katikati, mfano: ABC-123
Simama mbele tu ya mlango wa kuingia kwenye nyumba na ukusanye vipimo vya GPS vya eneo hilo
Subiri hadi accuracy itakapokuwa chini ya mita 6 au baada ya sekunde 60, chochote kitakacho kuja kwanza.
Voc tem um cdigo QR que contm seu cdigo de identifio?
Escreva aqui o seu cdigo de 3 digitos
### Informao Demografica e Identificao do chefe do agregado
Parece que voce esta em uma localidade nao listada na base de dados
Parece que voce esta em um bairro nao listada na base de dados
Confirme que este o cdigo do bairro em que voc esta
Confirme que este o cdigo do Bairro em que voc esta
Porque o bairro em que voce esta nao esta listado na nossa base de dados, o codigo sera "XXX". Voce deve contactar a sede antes de continuar.
Escreva o cdigo de agregado de 6 digitos aqui:
Inclua um traco no meio, por exemplo: ABC-123
Pare fora da porta principal da casa e tire as coordenadas geograficas do local.
Espere ate a precisao estar abaixo de 6m or 60 segundos, oque ocorrer primeiro
Do you have a QR code with your worker ID?
Manually write your 3 digit worker ID here
Scan your worker ID QR code
### Identification and demographic information of household and household head
What is the name of the village?
(You appear to be in a village which is not in the database)
What is the name of the hamlet?
(You appear to be in a hamlet which is not in the database)
Confirm that this is the hamlet code where you are
Confirm that this is the hamlet code where you are
Because the hamlet you are in is not in our database, the code will be "XXX". You should contact headquarters before continuing.
Include a dash in the middle, for example: ABC-123
Stand just outside the front door of the house and geocode the location.
Wait until accuracy is below 6m or 60 seconds, whichever comes first.

bind.jr:constraintMsg: The worker ID must be a number between 0 and 999, 3 digts, and can't start with a zero. / ID ya mfanyakazi lazima iwe kati ya 0 na 999, tarakamu 3, na haiwezi kuanza na sifuri. / O codigo do trabalhador deve ser um numero entre 0 e 999, 3 digitos, e nao pode comecar com zero.
ID must be in this format ABC-123 (only capital letters followed by a '-' and 3 numbers). Hii namba lazima iwe katika muundo wa ABC-123. Este numero deve estar no formato: ABC-123.
